<item>
            <title>[LU-7209] obdfilter-survey does not provide units</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7209</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Contrary to best practice, units are not provided in the output of &lt;br/&gt;
/usr/bin/obdfilter-survey&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;for example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Fri Sep 25 11:14:03 EDT 2015 Obdfilter-survey for case=disk from hds1fnb6123
ost 10 sz 167772160K rsz 1024K obj   10 thr   10 write 10982.73 [ 601.97,2912.91] rewrite 15696.54 [1160.92,3450.85] read 12358.60 [ 938.96,2634.87] 
ost 10 sz 167772160K rsz 1024K obj   10 thr   20 write 12560.84 [ 348.98,3021.92] rewrite 16390.31 [ 991.94,2311.88] read 12232.29 [ 814.98,2538.94] 
ost 10 sz 167772160K rsz 1024K obj   10 thr   40 write 14675.10 [ 861.96,1761.88] rewrite 12493.10 [ 484.98,1718.93] read 11821.92 [ 880.97,1942.85] 
ost 10 sz 167772160K rsz 1024K obj   10 thr   80 write 9325.18 [ 425.99,1684.93] rewrite 14249.78 [1050.76,1735.92] read 11767.79 [ 951.38,1765.93] 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sadly, the output is also not documented in the Operations Manual:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/lustre-manual/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/lustre_manual.xhtml#dbdoclet.50438212_26516&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.hpdd.intel.com/job/lustre-manual/lastSuccessfulBuild/artifact/lustre_manual.xhtml#dbdoclet.50438212_26516&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
